Quarter Final
Semi Finals
Portugal's Eus&lt;U+00E9&gt;bio won the tournament's Golden Boot scoring nine goals, six of them at Goodison Park.101 Eus&lt;U+00E9&gt;bio later stated that &quot;Goodison Park is for me the best stadium in my life&quot;.102 In Garrincha's 50 caps for Brazil, the only defeat he experienced was in the game versus Hungary at Goodison Park.103
FA Cup Final
Two years after construction, Goodison Park was chosen by the Football Association to host the final of the FA Cup.
